    <h1 class="insutrctions-title">WürfelTickTack<br/>“How to use it?”</h1>
    <h6>March, 2017 · Maja Kavčič</h6>
    <hr>
    <p class="opening-statement">
      „<strong>Würfelticktack</strong>“ is a didactic game used for practicing German language.
    </p>

    <strong>WürfelTickTack contents:</strong>
    <ol>
      <li>
        <a href="#contents" title="WürfelTickTack &mdash; contents">What's in the box?</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="#goals" title="WürfelTickTack &mdash; goals">WürfelTickTack goals</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="#game-variations" title="WürfelTickTack &mdash; game variations">Game variations</a>
      </li>
    </ol>

    <p>
      <br/>
      There is no time limit in playing this game. You are limited only when performing a speaking task, or in case you decide to use a sand clock as a time limit within which you perform a specific task. The game can be used in many different ways, both in writing and speaking. Do not forget that imagination and thinking outside the box are very important, if not the key features for easy and carefree learning.
    </p>

    <div class="cta-centered">
