    <h2><a class="internal-link" name="goals"></a>WürfelTickTack goals</h2>
    <blockquote>
      <p>
        Goals can be set according to the language level of the user.</p>
      <cite>&mdash;Maja Kavčič</cite>
    </blockquote>

    <p>
      Using this game you will not only learn new grammatical structures and vocabulary items in German, but you will also refresh, strengthen and upgrade your existing knowledge of German in a fun way.
    </p>

